lead_paragraph: Michael Conforto ended an 0-for-20 skid with an RBI single in the eighth and scored the tiebreaking run on pinch hitter Matt Reynolds' two-out single later in the inning to help the New York Mets rally past the Miami Marlins 6-4 on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Conforto's RBI in 8th Helps Mets Rally Past Marlins 6-4
